{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>John最近买了一个书架用来存放奶牛养殖书籍，但书架很快被存满了，只剩最顶层有空余。<p><p>John共有N头奶牛(1≤N≤20,000)，每头奶牛有自己的高度Hi(1≤Hi≤10,000)，N头奶牛的总高度为S。书架高度为B(1≤B≤S<2,000,000,007)。<p><p>为了到达书架顶层，奶牛可以踩着其他奶牛的背，像叠罗汉一样，直到他们的总高度不低于书架高度。当然若奶牛越多则危险性越大。为了帮助John到达书架顶层，找出使用奶牛数目最少的解决方案吧。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"书架 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>能达到书架高度所使用奶牛的最少数目。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第1行：空格隔开的整数N和B。<p><p>第2~N+1行：第i+1行为整数Hi。<p>","examples":"<input>6 40\n6\n18\n11\n13\n19\n11\n\n</input><output>3\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1228","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}